ComicInfo.Summary:
New readers start here! Jump on board with one of comics’ creative powerhouses – Prog 1926 sees the third episodes in the brand-new line-up of stunning stories! Dredd experiences the repercussions of the Titan penal revolt in Enceladus: New Life by Rob Williams and Henry Flint; Strontium Dog Johnny Alpha is given a mission to undertake if he's to save his friends from execution in Strontium Dog: The Stix Fix Job by John Wagner and Carlos Ezquerra; Celtic barbarian Sláine battles against the Drune Lords in the second book of The Brutania Chronicles, Primordial, by Pat Mills and Simon Davis; the Russian assassin Orlok finds a new mission in The Rasputin Caper by Arthur Wyatt and Jake Lynch; and things aren’t quite as they seem in Grey Area: Another Day On The Job by Dan Abnett and Mark Harrison.
